data.description: Don't miss this amazing opportunity to live in Stonebridge Ranch. 5 bedroom, Highland home located on a corner lot in the heart of Brightwood. It has a popular floor plan, with 2 bedrooms on the first level of the home & other flexible spaces traditionally dining or living spaces that can easily be converted into a dedicated study if desired. Open concept living where the kitchen & living space meet making it perfect for entertaining. a gas cooktop, granite countertops, & decorative light fixtures, & new carpet in the downstairs area. Upstairs there are 3 bedrooms & one that has a bathroom ensuite. Dedicated media room and playroom which is perfect for all. Walking distance to elementary school and restaurants. SBR HOA which includes multiple pools, tennis courts, community events, and more. 3 car garage & a large L-shaped yard, providing a side yard. W facing, located across the street from the walking trail. Amazing price for this home.
